Package guiClasses

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FarmView
    This class is what the user will see of the farm when playing the game
    SetupScreen
    This class is the window the user will first see when starting the game
    TownMap
    This class is a window of the town map, seen when playing the game
    WActions
    This class is the actions window, clicking the actions button from the farm opens this window
    WAnimalStore
    This class is a window for buying animals
    WCropStore
    This class is a window where the user buys crops
    WFeedAnimals
    This class is a window where the user can feed their animals
    WFinalScore
    This class is a window which is displayed when the game ends
    WindowManager
    This class is the main GUI manager window, this class brings all other classes together
    WItemStore
    This class is a window where the user can buy items
    WTendCrops
    This class is the window where the user can tend to their crops
